    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/fc10075125e71610d61f7c835630e0b4.poster.avif?t=1761224804\" width=576 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/fc10075125e71610d61f7c835630e0b4.webm?t=1761224804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/fc10075125e71610d61f7c835630e0b4.mp4?t=1761224804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《迷失幻境》是一款设定在90年代法国的故事驱动型动作冒险的角色扮演游戏，融合了黑暗元素。玩家将扮演迷失在神秘世界中的男孩西奥。探索独一无二的现实世界，运用独特快速的小游戏战斗系统对抗黑暗，并为自己的抉择负责。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/1c2632d7d0ab0c1f89f19d97f9d6ce38.avif?t=1761224804\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/e2ebe03f33f884e1d5a8808e4da925a7.poster.avif?t=1761224804\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/e2ebe03f33f884e1d5a8808e4da925a7.webm?t=1761224804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/e2ebe03f33f884e1d5a8808e4da925a7.mp4?t=1761224804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抛弃了传统RPG常见的菜单式战斗，《迷失幻境》采用了独特快速的小游戏战斗系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种敌人都有着不同的躲避方式和逐渐复杂的计时类小游戏，挑战性十足。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用独特的技能和装备，运筹帷幄，击败敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有随机遇敌机制（暗雷）。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/444cb6d6472ee22883537ae42b91e11c.avif?t=1761224804\" width=600 height=100 /></span>在一个夏季雨夜，西奥在自己的卧室醒来，却发现父母和妹妹路易丝都消失了。世界的真相逐渐显露，在西奥寻找妹妹的路途中，幽灵、幻影和怨灵于墓穴和黑暗之地不断出现，他总是慢一步，无法追上妹妹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一切究竟是怎么回事？这意味着什么？为什么这个地方如此熟悉？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >西奥的旅程由此展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/c2648388e0300da01219990b1f12d741.poster.avif?t=1761224804\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/c2648388e0300da01219990b1f12d741.webm?t=1761224804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/c2648388e0300da01219990b1f12d741.mp4?t=1761224804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/c6b89a0604f1c2b2fa24d8ce4583dabd.avif?t=1761224804\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式叙事</strong>带领玩家解开西奥的黑暗之谜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样化的场景</strong>：从充满生机祥和的氛围到黑暗神秘的场所，色彩丰富、环境变化多端。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>细腻考究的像素美术风格</strong>值得玩家细细探索。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>原创配乐</strong>：Nicolas Petton创作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的技能型战斗系统</strong>。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/154fcda7a9facb88d34f06c3b3833f86.poster.avif?t=1761224804\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/154fcda7a9facb88d34f06c3b3833f86.webm?t=1761224804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342600/extras/154fcda7a9facb88d34f06c3b3833f86.mp4?t=1761224804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
